WITH CTE_LEAD AS ( SELECT DATE_ID, MAKE_NAME, COUNT(DISTINCT LEAD_ID) AS UNIQUE_LEADS FROM DAILYSALES GROUP BY DATE_ID, MAKE_NAME ), CTE_PARTNER AS ( SELECT DATE_ID, MAKE_NAME, COUNT(DISTINCT PARTNER_ID) AS UNIQUE_PARTNERS FROM DAILYSALES GROUP BY DATE_ID, MAKE_NAME ) SELECT A.DATE_ID, A.MAKE_NAME, A.UNIQUE_LEADS, B.UNIQUE_PARTNERS FROM CTE_LEAD A INNER JOIN CTE_PARTNER B ON A.DATE_ID = B.DATE_ID AND A.MAKE_NAME = B.MAKE_NAME
